oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Greenback Presbyterian Church
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Edwin Best
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Greenback (Tenn.); Greenback Presbyterian Church;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Greenback Presbyterian Church, 1907-1952. The congregation was formed in 1908 and is still active. This describes the building and arrangement of the pulpit stage, choir stage and Sunday school rooms.
